				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: MB, kill in PoI, Need Help/info<a name="35572"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 20 04 11:09 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>
<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=10428">Manaetic Behemoth</a>
<br />

<br />
Spawn time: 3 days +/- a few hours
<br />

<br />
Map: <a target="_new" href="http://www.mapfiend.net/alldl.php">Download Maps</a>
<br />

<br />
Overview: 
<br />
Assemble your raid force just inside the entrance to the factory.  Form groups with standard MT group and dps groups as well as 4 CC groups.  The CC groups should have 1 mezzer and high dps.  The CC groups should be at the 4 corners that lead the spiders into MBs room.  When the raid is assembled and has been instructed everyone but the MT should be at the 4 corners killing spiders.  Once a sufficient number of spiders have been killed MB will become targetable.  This will be announced by the MT and the raid for should collect outside his door.  The CC groups will continue to CC the spiders.  If the spiders make it to MBs room they will explode for a 4k AoE DD, essentially wiping you.  So CC them by hook or crook.
<br />

<br />
Either have the MT engage immediately or a WS ranger.  Others may have a difference of opinion but I recommend centering MB in his room as opposed to cornering him.  Once MT has aggro and has called attack call it is max DPS time.  MB must die quickly or the spiders will wipe you.  Dead in 30seconds or so is ideal.  Casters should belly cast on him to avoid ping pong.  Cleric placement is key but I can't speak to that very well.
<br />

<br />
Upon his death, the gnome will spawn in room and be susceptible to the spiders AoE.  So he should immediately be pulled just outside the room by a monk or a bard.  People should hail for flag and relieve CC groups so they can hail.  
<br />

<br />
Key issues:
<br />
*CC groups must hold their corners
<br />
*Max DPS -- dead in 30 seconds
<br />
*Pull the gnome outside of the room immediately
<br />
*Its important for people to know their roles</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
